CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 24, 1952, pg. 27, reads: "It's and Art - That's what Steve Poole appears to be saying as he watches Sam Milai rack up another point in their semi-final match in YMCA Billiard Tournament. Milai, an easy winner in this match, ran into difficulty in the finals when he lost to Clarence Morris, 85 - 81."
TitMainTitle: Sam Milai aiming cue, with Steve Poole standing in background, for billiards tournament at Centre Avenue YMCA
